Class IDataCursorEnvelope

  • java.lang.Object
    • permafrost.tundra.data.IDataCursorEnvelope
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.wm.data.IDataCursor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CaseInsensitiveIData.CaseInsensitiveIDataCursor, CopyOnWriteIDataMap.CopyOnWriteIDataCursor, ImmutableIData.ImmutableIDataCursor

    public abstract class IDataCursorEnvelope
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.wm.data.IDataCursor
    Wraps an IDataCursor in an envelope object and provides a skeletal implementation for subclasses.
